Class YagoDbpediaMapping

  • java.lang.Object
    • code.dws.markovLogic.YagoDbpediaMapping

  • public class YagoDbpediaMapping
extends java.lang.Object
    this class creates yago to dbpedia mapping of classes. Important since this can complement scenarios where DBPedia type is missing
